---
import Title from "./ui/Title.astro";

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="w-full bg-linear-to-b from-[#F1EAFF] to-[#FFFFFF] text-gray-800">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-6">
      <img
        alt="Colegio Militarizado"
        class="h-40"
        src="/new.png"
      />
    </div>

    <Title tag="h5">•Honor •Disciplina •Trabajo</Title>

    <p class="text-center max-w-xl text-sm font-normal leading-relaxed">
      "Excelencia académica y disciplina para forjar a los líderes que Nuevo León y México necesitan."
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 text-center text-sm font-normal text-gray-700">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/528119061917"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="hover:text-green-700"
      >
        💬 +52 81 1906 1917
      </a>

      <a
        href="mailto:admin@colegiomilitarizadonl.com"
        class="hover:text-green-700"
      >
        admin@colegiomilitarizadonl.com
      </a>

      <p>
        Prol. Aztlán 9610, San Bernabé, 64217 Monterrey, N.L.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 text-center text-sm font-normal">
      <a href="https://codifika.mx">codifika.mx</a> ©{currentYear}
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
